All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable
public final class EnglishPossessiveFilter
extends TokenFilter

TokenFilter that removes possessives (trailing 's) from words.

You must specify the required Version compatibility when creating EnglishPossessiveFilter:

  • As of 3.6, U+2019 RIGHT SINGLE QUOTATION MARK and U+FF07 FULLWIDTH APOSTROPHE are also treated as quotation marks.
